# ARAF Standard — Copilot Instructions

## Project overview

This is the ARAF Standard website (araf-standard.org). It is a documentation site for an open governance standard built with Astro and the Starlight documentation framework, deployed to Netlify.

This is a standards body site, not a startup site. Write like NIST, W3C, or ISO — precise, institutional, no marketing language.

## Tech stack

- Framework: Astro with Starlight documentation theme
- Content: MDX files in `src/content/docs/`
- Config: `astro.config.mjs` controls sidebar and site settings
- Static assets: SVG logos and PDFs in `public/`
- Deployment: Netlify

